TextElement.Str: Activates game genie that can be accessed while gaming

Enabling Xmode max option set all x mode tunings found in armoury crate to max. So If you have already tuned the x mode parameters in armoury crate then dont use this option as it will override everything to max value

This app is a part of project Vulmax . Gaming mode comes with a lots of features which includes hardcore ram cleaner , pubg fps unlock , ping stabiliser , force lte only and also a game genie which is usually seen on gaming phones.
This app might not fit your screen because i made this app with my phone, not pc.
Chance of getting ban on pubg by using this app's fps unlock option is almost nil and is more safer than other third party apps available in playstore
If you failed to get 60 fps in pubg .reset this app from the 3 dot menu on main screen and try again
Join our telegram group for any suggestions or doubts
Check for the latest update on site
This app is completely free and will be .So if you like my work, you can support me
Disable the app from launch screen after you have finished game.
Gaming Mode needs to read your default pubg config.
Step 1: Uninstall /remove any other pubg config / gfx tool app if installed
Step 2: Open pubg play a tdm.
Step 3: After tdm is completed comeback here and press the read config button.
Note : Reset gaming mode app from options and try the steps again if you failed to get 60 fps unlock and texture compressions
For getting best results out of X mode you need to apply perfomance profile in vulmax app.
If you havent installed vulmax app , download from here
If you have already installed it. then apply perfomance profile to unlock X mode
